08:27.540 --> 08:29.041
Hey, I have one here.

08:29.108 --> 08:30.376
Not that one.

08:31.677 --> 08:34.547
Electronic devices
will be operational momentarily.

08:34.614 --> 08:36.915
Please contact the manufacturer
of your device

08:36.982 --> 08:38.650
should it not regain functionality.

08:38.717 --> 08:39.952
Go back inside!

08:40.385 --> 08:41.419
Get off the road!

08:46.859 --> 08:47.827
Female!

08:48.394 --> 08:49.629
Hispanic model!

08:52.798 --> 08:54.367
Fourth gen, female!

08:55.801 --> 08:57.870
