08:57.937 --> 08:59.705
Thank you for your cooperation.

09:11.117 --> 09:12.151
Got ya.

09:13.319 --> 09:14.453
Yeah, we got her.

09:15.454 --> 09:17.723
The simulate breach has been contained.

09:17.790 --> 09:20.459
Please stay inside and remain calm.
Thank you.

