Kept to herself mostly.

10:59.892 --> 11:02.094
Spoke to Mr. Rosen occasionally,

11:02.395 --> 11:04.764
you know, right next door 406.

11:04.830 --> 11:06.332
Nice man.

11:06.399 --> 11:07.800
He pays cash, too.

11:09.068 --> 11:10.236
